query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('activex',
'ajaxcontroltoolkit',
'android-testing',
'cpu-usage',
'guice',
'lifetime',
'point',
'pseudo-element',
'purrr',
'python-asyncio',
'searchview',
'spring-cloud',
'static-methods',
'swagger-ui',
'tvos');
